In the mystic traditions of the different religions we have a remarkable unity of spirit. Whatever religion they may profess, they are spiritual kinsmen. While the different religions in their historic forms bind us to limited groups and militate against the development of loyalty to the world community, the mystics have already stood for the fellowship of humanity in harmony with the spirit of the mystics of ages gone by.

Knowing that material & spiritual progress are essential to man, we must ceaselessly work for the equal attainment of both. Free my Nephew Namibia 🇳🇦! 
It’s been very long and this should be time served!! There’s no proof he’s guilty!!

#socialnationafrica #Mansu
#princeofHarlem #namibia 
#Jystice4kevan #Freekevantownsend
#BuriedAlive #bullet Harlem’s 5 Star General #freehim @ruckerparkstreetball
@usembnamibia

How ironic!! Taking part in the celebration of social nation Africa & The Mansa Floating Hub, performing on the day of my anniversary receiving My Hollywood Walk of Fame Star!!! 
That's when you know you are in your life's purpose!! I want to thank you all for your congrats and well wishes, from Africa!!!
@socialnationafrica @mansafloatinghub @bathilysvision @rogerpfrancis
I want to thank my children for reminding me of this special day!
